852
00:56:37,197 --> 00:56:38,198
Kau benar.

853
00:56:38,823 --> 00:56:42,410
Kita bicarakan lagi
setelah membangkitkan Bu Jang.

854
00:56:43,787 --> 00:56:44,829
Baiklah.

855
00:57:10,939 --> 00:57:12,107
